README File 
Week 3 Consolidation Task: Programme to Calculate Area of a Rectangle

**INTRODUCTION**
The programme is a CLI programme written in Python, which calculates the area of a rectangle (including squares).

**INSTALLATION**
The Python file can be downloaded and run directly.

Run the program with CLI on Windows:
python C:\path\to\Area_of_Rectangle_Calculator_Using_Loops_Consolidation_Task.py
The programme can also be run on a Python runtime software.

** INSTRUCTIONS **
Enter the values of the length and breath of the rectangle. The programme will request re-entry of these details if either is not a positive number. You can then re-enter the requested value.

The programme calculates the area of the rectangle (length times breadth)



